metadata.name: my alter enigma
metadata.description: i'm battling a reflection of my own, endlessly regenerating new versions of my defective selves. how do you fight your own reflection when heâ€™s the opposite of you? where is he? my grounds are his skies - my lows are his highs. abandon that version. cut him off. kill him off. do i need to be him to banish him? do i need to be the kind of evil i oppose to be for me to find him? will i remain as him once i do?
